data-triple-N3.o: "The Social Democratic Party of Switzerland (also rendered as Swiss Socialist Party; German: Sozialdemokratische Partei der Schweiz, SP; French: Parti socialiste suisse, PS; Italian: Partito Socialista Svizzero; Romansh: Partida Socialdemocrata de la Svizra) is a political party in Switzerland. The party was founded on 21 October 1888, and is currently the second largest of the four leading coalition political parties in Switzerland."@en
